## Gateway deploy checklist
1. `cd gateway && npm install`
2. Set Vercel env: SAVY_API_KEY, SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
3. `npx vercel --prod`
4. Copy deploy URL + API key into SAVY-Secrets.xcconfig
5. Rebuild iOS → status should flip to "Live AWS graph content"
